"text","text":"3. Carnation （red）—My heart aches for you; admiration.康乃馨"},{"type":"text","text":"（红色）——我的心为你而痛；赞赏。"},{"type":"text","text":"4. Carnation （purple）—Capriciousness. 康乃馨（紫色）——任"},{"type":"text","text":"性。"},{"type":"text","text":"5. Carnation （solid colour）—Yes. 康乃馨（纯色）——是。"}]},{"number":1889,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"6. Carnation （stripped）—No! refusal; sorry I can't be with you. 康"},{"type":"text","text":"乃馨（有斑纹）——不！拒绝；对不起，我不能和你在一起。"},{"type":"text","text":"7. Carnation （white）—Sweet and lovely; innocence; pure love;"},{"type":"text","text":"good luck. 康乃馨（白色）——甜蜜而可爱；天真无邪；纯洁的爱；好"},{"type":"text","text":"运。"},{"type":"text","text":"8. Carnation （yellow）—You have disappointed me; rejection.康乃"},{"type":"text","text":"馨（黄色）——你让我感到失望；拒绝。"}]}]}